
You need to subscript redhat linux in order to use yum ...

 

step:

 

1ï¼Œ [root@localhost ~]# subscription-manager register

 

2, type your redhat developer account and password

   Username: pengchao.ma2@outlook.com

   Password: **********

 

3, [root@localhost ~]# subscription-manager attach --auto

 

4, check your subscription

   [root@localhost ~]# subscription-manager status

 

5, run yum update -y

 

   [root@localhost ~]# yum update -y

 

done!

 

 
